-- Fiat's Car Components Maker Magneti Marelli Aiming to Expand in Russia
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-11-10T11:12:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/fiat-s-car-components-maker-magneti-marelli-aiming-to-expand-in-russia.html
Fiat SpA’s Magneti Marelli auto-
parts division aims to expand in Russia where it wants to become
“a leading player,” Chief Executive officer Eugenio Razelli
said today in a statement.  Magneti Marelli opened today a lighting plant in Ryazan,
southeast of Moscow, which will produce 2 million pieces a year
at full capacity.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  